{{!< layouts/main}}

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="page-header-content">
    <div>
      <h1>{{pageTitle}}</h1>
      <p class="text-muted">Discuss sports, matches, and strategies</p>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary">+ New Post</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="forum-categories">
  <button class="category-btn active">All</button>
  <button class="category-btn">Cricket</button>
  <button class="category-btn">Match Discussion</button>
  <button class="category-btn">Tips & Strategies</button>
  <button class="category-btn">Off-topic</button>
</div>

<div class="forum-posts">
  <div class="post-card">
    <div class="post-votes">
      <button class="vote-btn up">▲</button>
      <span class="vote-count">24</span>
      <button class="vote-btn down">▼</button>
    </div>
    <div class="post-content">
      <h3><a href="#">Best batting techniques for T20 cricket?</a></h3>
      <p>Looking for tips on improving my strike rate in T20 matches. What techniques do you recommend for power hitting?</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="author">by CricketFan99</span>
        <span class="category">Tips & Strategies</span>
        <span class="time">2 hours ago</span>
        <span class="comments">12 comments</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="post-card">
    <div class="post-votes">
      <button class="vote-btn up active">▲</button>
      <span class="vote-count">45</span>
      <button class="vote-btn down">▼</button>
    </div>
    <div class="post-content">
      <h3><a href="#">Match Analysis: Team Alpha vs Team Beta</a></h3>
      <p>Great match yesterday! Let's discuss the key moments and turning points. That catch in the 18th over was incredible!</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="author">by MatchAnalyst</span>
        <span class="category">Match Discussion</span>
        <span class="time">5 hours ago</span>
        <span class="comments">28 comments</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="post-card">
    <div class="post-votes">
      <button class="vote-btn up">▲</button>
      <span class="vote-count">8</span>
      <button class="vote-btn down">▼</button>
    </div>
    <div class="post-content">
      <h3><a href="#">New to cricket - where to start?</a></h3>
      <p>Just started playing cricket. Any recommendations for beginner drills and equipment?</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="author">by NewPlayer2024</span>
        <span class="category">Cricket</span>
        <span class="time">1 day ago</span>
        <span class="comments">15 comments</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .page-header-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .forum-categories {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .category-btn {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  .category-btn.active {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    border-color: var(--primary);
  }
  .forum-posts {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .post-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .post-votes {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    min-width: 40px;
  }
  .vote-btn {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 0.25rem;
  }
  .vote-btn:hover, .vote-btn.active { color: var(--primary); }
  .vote-count { font-weight: 600; }
  .post-content { flex: 1; }
  .post-content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .post-content h3 a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .post-content h3 a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
  .post-content p {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  .post-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .post-meta .category {
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
</style>
